sources.title: SUNDOWN video quality upgrade
sources.description: This glitch-free print is much sharper than the existing IA copies. “Solid drama with interesting settings and a good cast” “Good 1940’s entertainment” “Could Gene Tierney be any more beautiful?” (IMDB reviews quotes). Intrigue and adventure set in wartime British East Africa with a solid cast and excellent production values. Nominated for three Oscars (cinematography, art direction, music scoring). Released 39 days before the US entry into WW 2. IMDB rating 5.8. Directed by Henry Hathaway. Released in 1941. Complete print.
